comments: Crowder (MIA) makes incidental contact with Fultz (ORL) as they mutually engage during the rebound.
Robinson (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Ross' (ORL) jump shot.
Fultz (ORL) places his hand to Dragic's (MIA) front and makes marginal contact with Dragic's (MIA) arm as he rips through.
Ross (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Crowder's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
Fournier (ORL) maintains clean hand on ball contact during Butler's (MIA) driving shot attempt and a jump-ball is correctly assessed.
Adebayo (MIA) and Fultz (ORL) makes incidental contact as they move in the same direction to retrieve the loose ball.
Vucevic (ORL) makes marginal contact with Adebayo (MIA) at the start of the drive however, Adebayo (MIA) is able to move along his desired path.
Fultz (ORL) briefly grasps Butler's (MIA) arm during the rebound however, Butler (MIA) is able to move through the contact to retrieve the ball.
As Fournier (ORL) legally contest Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt, Butler (MIA) slightly extends his legs out creating marginal contact with Fournier's (ORL) lower body.
Fultz (ORL) fails to inbound the ball within five seconds.
Vucevic (ORL) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Iguodala's (MIA) path and absorbs the contact.
Iguodala (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt and avoids making contact with  Vucevic's (ORL) arm during his upward shooting motion.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Gordon's (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Gordon (ORL) maintains a legal guarding position while defending Bulter's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
As Vucevic (ORL) moves naturally to retrieve the ball during the rebound, he makes incidental contact with Adebayo's (MIA) face.
Fournier (ORL) slightly extends his off-arm to Jones Jr.'s (MIA) front, and as Fournier is removing his arm, Jones Jr. makes brief contact with Fournier's off-arm but does not affect his SQBR.
Crowder (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Gordon's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
